get...listen carefully---Give whatever you want to whomever you want, but make sure there is at least some semblance of balance.</P><P>Frankly, so far it isn't there.</P><P>EDIT: SK's won't cast cascading for the same reasons we won't. So why'd they give it to us in the first place huh?</P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=264137" target="_blank" target="_blank">Charbonez Soulmark</a><BR>Clan Doomit<BR>Duzzil Ro</P><P>Edited by - charbonez on 09/24/2002  13:14:01</font></td>
